          The 2022 fantasy baseball season has arrived, but many leagues will be holding their drafts over this first weekend of play. If you're one of those fantasy managers, surely you're still finalizing your list of which players you want to draft for your teams. The following rankings are designed specifically with ESPN roto-style leagues in mind.

          Please note that these rankings reflect what we think players will do in the upcoming season and not how they may have performed in previous campaigns. Starting next week, we will transition these rankings to reflect fantasy production for the rest of the season.

          To see rankings and cheat sheets for all types of leagues, visit the ESPN Draft Kit. Additionally, sign up for ESPN Fantasy Baseball today!

          Note: Tristan H. Cockcroft's points league rankings can be found here.
